data.description: Beautiful, Amazing home located in the Vinemont school district.  This home sits on a beautiful acre of land.  Home features 3bedrooms/2baths, open concept living/dining/kitchen, split bedroom floor plan, hard wood throughout the home, vinyl tile in bathrooms and laundry room, plantation blinds, granite countertops, large pantry in kitchen and pantry in laundry area, large 1 car garage with storm safety shelter, and a covered screened in patio with an open area uncovered.  There is a nice storage building as well.  The driveway is concrete with extra concrete on the side of the home for extra parking.  Imagine yourself on the front porch or the back screened porch relaxing drinking tea or coffee!  This home has been well maintained and is ready for it's new owners.
